                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-pad up</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Right view down (through 90°):
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-pad down</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Right view left (through 90°):
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-pad left</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Right view right (through 90°):
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-pad right</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Move plane:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Left Analog Stick</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Area view:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Right Analog Stick</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Rear view:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R3 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Switch lock on target (or hold down to direct rpc to selected target):
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Fire missile:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Fire machine gun:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; View map / Zoom radar:
